Benefits of Solar Energy
=========================

### Benefits Summary

Solar energy provides several benefits, including:

* Reducing reliance on fossil fuels and improving air quality
* Saving money on electricity bills over its lifespan
* Lowering dependence on utility companies
* Providing a sustainable source of energy for homes

### Long-term Savings

Installing solar panels can save homeowners $25,000 to over $110,000 over its lifetime.

### Environmental Benefits

Solar energy reduces the environmental impact of homes by lowering their reliance on grid-supplied power.